(69, 1, '2020-03-11 13:19:42', '2020-03-11 13:19:42', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nCreate Sound Shortcut on Windows 10 Desktop</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A shortcut of Sound can help you open the Sound window (see the following picture) at the top speed. Now, read on to find how to create Sound shortcut on desktop in Windows 10 computer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Video guide on how to create Sound shortcut on Windows 10 desktop:<br>Steps to create Sound shortcut on Windows 10 desktop:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step 1: Right-click the desktop, point at New on the context menu and tap Shortcut in the sub-menu to open a new shortcut.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step 2: Type %windir%\\system32\\mmsys.cpl and tap Next in the Create Shortcut window.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NOTE: You can replace \'mmsys.cpl\' with any other Control Panel item located in \'%windir%\\system32\\\' whose extension is \'.cpl\'.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step 3: Enter Sound and choose Finish in the following window.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you can see from the screen shot below, a shortcut named Sound is displayed on the desktop.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isunshare.com/windows-10/create-sound-shortcut-on-windows-10-desktop.html\">https://www.isunshare.com/windows-10/create-sound-shortcut-on-windows-10-desktop.html</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Shortcut to Windows Control Panel Items', 'You might be using some Windows control panel items so frequently that you might want to place them somewhere more easily accessible. This guide will help you with that. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shortcut-to-windows-control-panel-items', '', '', '2020-03-11 13:19:42', '2020-03-11 13:19:42', '', 0, 'http://mywebsite.test/?p=69', 0, 'post', '', 0),
