(3, 3, 'category', 'These are probably the most compelling reasons why I decided to run a website; to expose my ideas.', 0, 0),
(4, 4, 'category', 'What I have learnt, the way I have learnt. These are shared to make later similar journeys easier and faster.', 0, 0),
(5, 5, 'category', 'Messing around with your computer, you sometimes realize you have come along a path which might well be trodden by many others in the future. In that case, it will be very helpful to note down the process.', 4, 7),
