(13, 13, 'category', 'Teaching English as a second language has never been off my career. As part of my career, this website is not an exception.', 0, 0),
(14, 14, 'category', 'My whole teaching experience has been with Iranian students. People from the same mother language tend to make similar mistakes while learning a foreign language. These tips might turn out to be very helpful for Iranians who are trying to learn English.', 13, 0),
(15, 15, 'category', 'I just cannot help crossing lines. Hope you don\'t mind while you read these. ', 3, 1),
